question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: Wat is de naam van het administratieve centrum van Cēsu novads (provincie Cēsis) in Letland?
answer: Het administratieve centrum van Cēsu novads in Letland is de stad Cēsis.
answer_translated_eng: The administrative centre of Cēsu novads in Latvia is the town of Cēsis.
